title: MU-TE-LUV
overview: The MU-NIVERSE franchise features seven series, including "Hi" By My Luck, Not My Father, Diva Deva Mata starring Fluke Nattanon, Fist Foot Fusion, Hello' Is This Luck?, Love Me If You Swear, and Love Lock.  Each story portrays a unique journey to finding love. Will the higher power help turn their luck around? Will their wishes be granted?
